      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.9550564925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の里帰りライブを\nあのシーパラで行うことが決まりましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been decided that our homecoming live\nwill be held at that Sea Paradise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9550564925,
      "endTime": 12.612109295500002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7849668025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、期間中は私達、月ストとサニピが\nシーパラを乗っ取ることになりましたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ during the period‚ we Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace\nwill be taking over Sea Paradise!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7849668025,
      "endTime": 20.891384267699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0975745994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "乗っ取りじゃなくて、コラボですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a takeover‚ it's a collaboration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0975745994,
      "endTime": 24.145919259200003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.3309079328
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、里帰りライブを更に盛り上げるために\nみなさんにはコラボ企画を考えていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ to make the homecoming live even more exciting‚\nwe'd like everyone to think of collaboration ideas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3309079328,
      "endTime": 31.6917695203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.897959852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ここで考えたアイデアが\nシーパラコラボで実現するかもしれないんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ideas we come up with here\nmight actually be realized in the Sea Paradise collaboration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.897959852,
      "endTime": 38.0476421831,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.2538325148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事が忙しくて全員揃うのは無理でしたが……\nまずはこの六人で会議をいたしますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone couldn't gather because work is busy…\nbut first‚ we'll have a meeting with these six people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2538325148,
      "endTime": 47.1029257613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3091160931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "やりたい企画がある人は奮って発言してくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyone with project ideas‚ please speak up actively!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3091160931,
      "endTime": 51.8472113766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.0534017083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "まずはスタンプラリーですね。これは外せません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First is a stamp rally. This is indispensable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0534017083,
      "endTime": 56.0135832307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.220068375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "スタンプラリーは前回もやったわよね？\n今回はやらなくてもいいんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We did a stamp rally last time too‚ didn't we?\nI think we don't need to do it this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.220068375,
      "endTime": 62.0812704243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.287460756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……この世にやらなくていいスタンプラリーは\nありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…There is no stamp rally in this world that doesn't need\nto be done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.287460756,
      "endTime": 66.32754778820001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.5207905289
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "目つきが怖いわよ……そんなにムキにならなくても\nスタンプラリーはちょっとしたお遊び的なものだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your expression is scary… you don't need to get so worked up.\nA stamp rally is just a little game…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5207905289,
      "endTime": 74.7956432816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9018320874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "スタンプラリーは遊びじゃありません！\nスタンプラリーは……人生です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stamp rallies are not games!\nStamp rallies are… life!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9018320874,
      "endTime": 80.4870927648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7018320874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、逆らっちゃダメだよ\n沙季ちゃんはスタンプラリーガチ勢なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚ you shouldn't oppose her.\nSaki-chan is hardcore about stamp rallies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7018320874,
      "endTime": 88.0042582349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2018320874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "スタンプラリーガチ勢……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hardcore about stamp rallies…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2018320874,
      "endTime": 91.19108374870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3972740805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "今回は私が全面的にプロデュースします\n皆さんに、真のスタンプラリーをお見せします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time I'll produce it completely.\nI'll show everyone a true stamp rally!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3972740805,
      "endTime": 99.6818092978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.8639407471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "次は私……私もシーパラで……\nお客さんとやりたいことがある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is me… I also want to do something\nwith the customers at Sea Paradise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8972740805,
      "endTime": 107.6699045813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.8639407471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんは水族館で何をやりたいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want to do at the aquarium‚ Shizuku-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8639407471,
      "endTime": 111.6020031765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.7972740805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "魚釣り……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fishing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7972740805,
      "endTime": 113.4516973651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.663942273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "水族館で魚釣ったらダメだよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can't fish at the aquarium!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.663942273,
      "endTime": 116.91024611750001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0972756064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、分かってない……\nシーパラには魚釣りが出来る『うみファーム』がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ you don't understand…\nSea Paradise has \"Umi Farm\" where you can fish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0972756064,
      "endTime": 123.60562006590001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
