      "text": "お疲れ様です。……{user}さん？\n何を見てるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. …{user}-san?\nWhat are you looking at?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.5208160153,
      "endTime": 263.1724486103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これか？　これは沙季が作ってくれた議事録だよ\n今日の昼間に、沙季達が会議をしていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This? This is the meeting minutes that Saki made for us.\nSaki and the others had a meeting this afternoon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.3786389421,
      "endTime": 270.7057819437,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7533.33333339998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "シーパラコラボの企画会議ですね。沢山案が出てる！\n私は仕事で参加出来ませんでしたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Sea Paradise collaboration planning meeting. So many ideas!\nI couldn't participate because of work‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.9119722755,
      "endTime": 280.0911562355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言えば、この間作ったセトリは結局\nどうなったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ what happened to the setlist\nwe made the other day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.2973282567,
      "endTime": 285.0453739872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それが、イベントの都合で二曲までしか歌えないから\nもう一度、何を歌うか決めてもらっていいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ because of the event schedule‚ you can only sing two songs‚\nso could you decide again which ones to sing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.251564319,
      "endTime": 292.86248169649997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "二曲まで……それだとあのセトリは使えないですね\nまたみんなで話し合って決め直さないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Up to two songs… then that setlist can't be used.\nI'll have to discuss and decide again with everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.051552112,
      "endTime": 302.750531299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "昼の部と夜の部で歌う曲を変えてもいいぞ\n後、イルカショーで使う曲も考えておいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can change the songs between the afternoon and evening shows.\nAlso‚ please think about the song to use for the dolphin show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.9567216308,
      "endTime": 309.8023907096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "やることが山積みですね。でも自分達でイベントを\n作り上げていく感じがして、準備するのも楽しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a mountain of things to do. But the feeling of\ncreating the event ourselves makes even the preparation fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.9900549641,
      "endTime": 319.7975155582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに加えてコラボも決まって大変だと思うが\nみんなの希望が最大限叶うように俺も努めるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's tough with the collaboration decided in addition to the live‚\nbut I'll also work to fulfill everyone's wishes as much as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.00370589,
      "endTime": 327.1042272637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "シーパラとコラボするのも三度目だからな\n俺も勝手は分かっているつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is also the third time collaborating with Sea Paradise‚\nso I think I understand how things work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.30370589,
      "endTime": 332.90749264469997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "三度目？　シーパラコラボは二度目じゃ……\nあ、もしかして、一回目はお姉ちゃんの時ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Third time? Isn't this the second Sea Paradise collaboration…\nAh‚ could it be that the first time was during my sister's time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.10370589,
      "endTime": 343.447175319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。あの頃は俺もまだ新人で\nコラボに慣れていなくて四苦八苦したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Back then I was still a newcomer\nand I wasn't used to collaborations— so I struggled a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.6533656508,
      "endTime": 350.1014607817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃんがシーパラとコラボした時のこと\n良ければ教えてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Would you mind telling me about the time\nmy sister collaborated with Sea Paradise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.2866989841,
      "endTime": 355.9053611507,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}